measurements.description: Twenty-four flowers and 16 buds spherically presented on two upright 9-cm inflorescences; flowers white; petals overlaid bold purple centrally, white picotee; lip trilobed, sidelobes overlaid purple centrally, leaving white edges, central lobe bold purple, white picotee, nectary white, 0.7cm ; substance firm; texture velvet; commended for strong lip color.
